OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,FFirefighters are facing "challenging
OL,7,Fconditions" as a massive wildfire
OL,8,Ftears through moorland, forcing
OL,9,Femergency services to declare a major
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FDerbyshire Fire & Rescue Service
OL,13,F(DFRS) confirmed the move late on
OL,14,FSunday, 12 July, following the rapid
OL,15,Fspread of the blaze at Tintwistle Moor
OL,16,Fon the Derbyshire-Greater Manchester
OL,17,Fborder - first reported on 24 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
