OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,FAn area equivalent to 350 football
OL,7,Fpitches has already been destroyed,
OL,8,Fwith multiple crews and specialist
OL,9,Fresources from across the region
OL,10,Fdrafted in to battle the flames which
OL,11,Fhave been burning for almost three
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FWhile active firefighting operations
OL,15,Fare pausing overnight, officials say
OL,16,Fthe scale of the incident means
OL,17,Foperations will resume first thing on
OL,18,FMonday morning and are expected to
OL,19,Flast "for some time".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,FArea Manager Ellie Gillatt described
OL,7,Fthe wildfire as a protracted situation
OL,8,Frequiring a massive, multi-agency
OL,9,Fresponse.
OL,11,F"Firefighters continue to face
OL,12,Fchallenging conditions as they work to
OL,13,Ftackle the wildfire and protect the
OL,14,Fsurrounding infrastructure and
OL,15,Fenvironment," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
