FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,F"This remains a significant and
OL,7,Fcomplex incident... DFRS has deployed
OL,8,Fmultiple fire appliances and
OL,9,Fspecialist wildfire resources,
OL,10,Fsupported by neighbouring fire and
OL,11,Frescue services and partner agencies."
OL,13,FA large-scale team is currently on the
OL,14,Fscene, including the Peak District
OL,15,FFire Operations Group, United
OL,16,FUtilities, Derby Mountain Rescue, and
OL,17,FDerbyshire Constabulary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
