OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,FWith smoke visible for miles,
OL,7,Femergency services are urging local
OL,8,Fresidents and visitors to take
OL,9,Fimmediate precautions by avoiding the
OL,10,Farea and keeping windows and doors
OL,11,Ffirmly shut.
OL,13,FThe service warned that the recent
OL,14,Fheatwaves mean conditions are tinder
OL,15,Fdry and wildfires can spark and spread
OL,16,Fwith "devastating" speed.
OL,18,FOfficials are renewing urgent safety
OL,19,Fcalls, pleading with the public to
OL,20,Fbehave responsibly in the countryside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
