FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor incident as huge wildfire burns
OL,4,Carea size of 350 football pitches
OL,6,FThanking the public and emergency
OL,7,Fstaff for their resilience, Area
OL,8,FManager Gillatt added: "We appreciate
OL,9,Fthe continued patience and co-
OL,10,Foperation of our communities at this
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"We would also like to extend a thanks
OL,14,Fto our firefighters, control staff and
OL,15,Fpartner agencies whose tireless
OL,16,Fefforts and dedication are helping to
OL,17,Fbring this incident to the safest and
OL,18,Fmost effective conclusion possible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
